8 SENATE AMENDMENT “ ” to COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “A” to S.P. 661,
9 L.D. 1667, “Resolve, to Allow Hemphill Farms, Inc. to Sue the State”
10 Amend the amendment in the first instructional paragraph in the 4th line (page 1, line
11 14 in amendment) by striking out the following: "$2,500,000" and inserting the following:
12 '$400,000'
13 Amend the amendment by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or
14 section number to read consecutively.
15 SUMMARY
1166 This amendment amends Committee Amendment "A" by reducing the maximum value
1177 of an award of damages resulting from the civil action authorized by the resolve from
1188 $2,500,000 to $400,000.
